<view class="page-shell pay-info-page">
  <section-title
    title="支付与确认说明"
    desc="本期默认关闭真实在线支付，提交后请联系客服人工确认预约信息。"
  ></section-title>

  <view class="card pay-info-card" wx:if="{{order}}">
    <view class="pay-info-card__top">
      <view class="pay-info-card__main">
        <text class="pay-info-card__order-no">订单号 {{order.orderNo}}</text>
        <text class="pay-info-card__amount">应付金额 ￥{{order.payableAmount}}</text>
      </view>
      <status-badge status="{{order.status}}" tone="{{order.tone}}"></status-badge>
    </view>

    <view class="pay-info-card__items">
      <text class="pay-info-card__item" wx:for="{{order.items}}" wx:key="id">{{item.displayName}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card pay-info-card">
    <text class="pay-info-card__title">当前支付方式</text>
    <text class="pay-info-card__desc" wx:if="{{!canOnlinePay}}">
      在线支付暂未开通，订单已创建，请联系客服确认排单和后续流程。
    </text>
    <text class="pay-info-card__desc" wx:else>
      当前环境已允许在线支付，可在后续接入 requestPayment 真实流程。
    </text>
    <text class="pay-info-card__desc">支付模式：{{paymentMode}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card pay-info-card">
    <text class="pay-info-card__title">联系客服</text>
    <button
      wx:if="{{useContactButton}}"
      class="ghost-button"
      open-type="contact"
    >
      打开客服会话
    </button>
    <button
      wx:else
      class="ghost-button"
      bindtap="handleContactFallback"
      hover-class="is-pressing"
      hover-stay-time="150"
    >
      查看客服说明
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="pay-info-page__actions">
    <button
      class="primary-button"
      bindtap="handleViewOrders"
      hover-class="is-pressing"
      hover-stay-time="150"
    >
      查看订单列表
    </button>
    <button
      class="ghost-button"
      bindtap="handleBackService"
      hover-class="is-pressing"
      hover-stay-time="150"
    >
      返回服务页
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
